Grandmas custard ice cream
==========================
makes 1 quart
* 1c milk, scalding hot
* 2T cornstarch
* pinch salt
* 3/4c suger
add scalding milk to other ingredients and
cook over medium heat until thickened (10 min)
* 2 eggs
mix a small amount of the hot mixture into 
beaten eggs, then slowly add eggs into hot 
mixture.  cook for 1 additional minute.
Allow mixture to cool
* 2c cream
* 1-1/2t vanilla
Stir in cream and vanilla.  Freeze per 
ice-cream makers directions.  